---
// Homepage-element dat verwijst naar /quickscan: links de propositie, rechts een mockup van het resultaatscherm.
---

<section class="relative py-24 overflow-hidden border-t border-primary-100/60" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, #eff8ff 0%, #f8fbff 100%);">
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-accent-400/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/4 pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- Copy -->
      <div data-reveal="0">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-600 mb-3">Gratis quickscan</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-primary-950 tracking-tight leading-tight">
          Waar sta jij op weg naar <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text" style="background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #0e2470 0%, #196bd7 50%, #01a2e8 100%);">certificering?</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-primary-900/70 leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
          Beantwoord 12 korte vragen en zie direct welke aanpak bij jouw organisatie past, hoe lang het traject duurt en waar je moet beginnen.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-7 space-y-3.5">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-primary-900/80">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 text-emerald-600 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span>Direct resultaat op je scherm, in 3 minuten</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-primary-900/80">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 text-emerald-600 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span>Persoonlijk advies: route, abonnement en doorlooptijd</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-primary-900/80">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 text-emerald-600 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span>Inclusief de gratis ISO Startgids (pdf) om intern te delen</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mt-9 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
          <a href="/quickscan" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-950 bg-accent-400 hover:bg-accent-500 hover:text-white rounded-xl transition-all shadow-lg shadow-accent-500/25">
            Doe de gratis quickscan
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/></svg>
          </a>
          <span class="text-sm text-primary-900/50">Geen account nodig · alle vier de ISO-normen</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Mockup resultaatscherm -->
      <div class="relative max-w-md mx-auto w-full lg:max-w-none" data-reveal="140">
        <div class="absolute -top-8 -right-8 w-64 h-64 bg-primary-400/15 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
        <a href="/quickscan" class="relative block bg-white rounded-3xl border border-primary-100 shadow-2xl shadow-primary-900/10 overflow-hidden transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 lg:rotate-1 lg:hover:rotate-0">
          <div class="h-1.5" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0e2470 0%, #196bd7 50%, #01a2e8 100%);"></div>
          <div class="px-7 py-4 bg-primary-50/70 border-b border-primary-100 flex items-center justify-between">
            <p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-500">Jouw resultaat</p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[11px] font-semibold text-emerald-700 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              Scan afgerond
            </span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-7">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
              <div class="relative w-28 h-28 shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-28 h-28 -rotate-90" viewBox="0 0 120 120">
                  <defs>
                    <linearGradient id="qsb-donut" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1">
                      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#196bd7"/>
                      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#01a2e8"/>
                    </linearGradient>
                  </defs>
                  <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="50" fill="none" stroke="#e9effb" stroke-width="12"/>
                  <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="50" fill="none" stroke="url(#qsb-donut)" stroke-width="12" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-dasharray="314" stroke-dashoffset="182"/>
                </svg>
                <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
                  <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-950 leading-none">42%</p>
                  <p class="mt-0.5 text-[9px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-400">staat al</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-500 mb-1">Aanbevolen route</p>
                <p class="text-lg font-bold text-primary-950 leading-snug">Zelfstandig met vangnet</p>
                <p class="mt-1.5 text-xs text-primary-500">Jouw startpositie: de basis is er, nu structureren</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
              <div class="rounded-xl bg-primary-50/70 border border-primary-100 px-4 py-3">
                <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-500">Abonnement</p>
                <p class="mt-0.5 text-sm font-bold text-primary-950">Team · € 199/mnd</p>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-xl bg-primary-50/70 border border-primary-100 px-4 py-3">
                <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-500">Doorlooptijd</p>
                <p class="mt-0.5 text-sm font-bold text-primary-950">3 tot 5 maanden</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-dashed border-primary-200 px-4 py-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0113.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375H8.25m2.25 0H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 00-9-9z"/></svg>
              <p class="text-xs text-primary-900/70"><strong class="text-primary-950">De ISO Startgids</strong> als gratis download bij je resultaat</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
